{"tid":2377110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵與 Alipay 合作　推出二維碼付費乘車","createTime":"2021-01-23T10:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T10:58:01.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7582e2b897c0ffb1ea44d0425fbea54600ad056f","tid":2377110,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n【港鐵與 Alipay 合作　推出二維碼付費乘車】<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，已經與阿里巴巴旗下支付商 AlipayHK 合作，推出二維碼付費乘車服務，今日（23 日）正式在機場快綫車站外的 93 個重鐵車站，於每一排閘機最少設置兩部閘機可作二維碼付費乘車。港鐵表示，乘客未來可利用二維碼，以銀聯、微信支付等方式付費乘車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司商務總監楊美珍表示，二維碼乘搭港鐵是一個重要的里程碑，公司將引入更多付費形式，令整個港鐵乘車體驗更智能化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pCWwza3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpCWwza3.jpg&h=815dda23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b179103324d29c336ca75b73bcf0e1addb21116a","tid":2377110,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:25:22.000Z","msg":"弱智化就係"},{"pid":"413ee083aee8230dbcf235c7dee6042daeb011ed","tid":2377110,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:26:09.000Z","msg":"我淨係覺得好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42b96de7b71b592d0ec0491a49f48599f394585","tid":2377110,"uid":130177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"拍一嘢就得嘅嘢<br />\n出QR曲都唔知做咩撚"},{"pid":"2fd783fbf2f2ff2a4d614862b810988a064b985e","tid":2377110,"uid":172233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"真心就算唔係因為反國貨，我都覺呢個idea難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時用支啦寶買野己經慢，交通工具咁多人仲慢慢開apps掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0602044a53c05f51cb54fc0f74aba9b965c629","tid":2377110,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"慢都唔係最大問題<br />\n都冇交通津貼，連藍絲都唔會用啦"},{"pid":"c9676e33ac5bf2976e8bd9715a58abad1776